RACE.RACE_TEXT: Texas Lone Star Juvenile S. - Grade3 LONE STAR PARK RACE 2 6F Dirt CR: 82. Stakes Purse 32750. FOR ARABIAN THREE YEAR OLDS. No nomination fee, $250 to pass the entry box and an additional $250 to start. Supplemental nomination of $2,000 is due at the time of entry and includes all fees. The added monies and all fees are to be divided 60% to the owner of the winner, 20% to second, 10% to third, 6% to fourth, 4% to fifth after sixth through tenth are paid $1,000 each. If less than ten horses start, the purse monies not awarded will revert to the winning owner. Weight: 122 lbs. Non-winners oft wo races in 2023 allowed 2 lbs; a race in 2023, 4 lbs. (Maiden and Claiming races not considered in allowances). Starters to be named through the entry box by the usual time of closing. Preference given to original nominations with the highest earnings. The field will be limited to twelve starters. Horses not drawing a starting position in the gate will receive a refund of the entry fee. A trophy will be presented to the winning owner.
